sub_title: MD at Eggs for Congo SARL
summary:
Started in 1980 in the poultry sector as entrepreneur and in 1990 started the trade in animal feed for exotic animals. 

Anno 2014 the company has grown to an international operating trading company with offices in United Kingdom and Spain. We specialize in special diet feeds for exotic animals and producer of natural feed for dogs and cats.

On personal title and Corporate Social Responsibility with the companies I started anno 2010 the foundation Etike in Kinshasa, Congo. This foundation provides shelter, education and healthcare for teenage mothers and their children. Resulting my contacts in Congo I'm also developing activities 
to stimulate the economy of Kinshasa and to create a self supporting system for the foundation.
